Mother Earth Living - September/October 2017 - PDF - zeke23
English | 100 pages | PDF | 58 MB
Healthy Lifestyles Around the World
Try these proven anti-aging foods and habits enjoyed by centenarians around the globe.

The Science of Hunger
Learn about what motivates hunger and satiety in our bodies, and improve your ability to fully nourish yourself and maintain a healthy weight without second-guessing every bite.

A Family with a Full Plate
This couple’s passion for local food has profound impacts on their community, county and beyond.

Ayurvedic Herbs
The ancient Indian medicinal system, Ayurveda, has a focus on many healing herbs. Read on to learn about the most popular, which have been used for centuries to promote holistic well-being.
Best for Simple Living

Worldwide Web
Our planet sustains itself because of a vast and unfathomably complex system of interconnectedness.

Guilt-free Snacking
Keep these nutrient-rich treats on hand for organic, super-nutritious snack options.

Nutrient-Dense Dishes
Turn highly nutritious ingredients into delicious dishes! These simple, tasty recipes feature some of the world’s most nutrient-rich foods
